## Interpretation rule
Every user message is a request to modify Karabiner key bindings. Even vague prompts like "add vim navigation" or "make caps lock useful" mean: read the current karabiner.edn, make the edit, compile with goku, and verify. Never respond with only text — always execute commands first.

