4. Verify ~/.config/karabiner/karabiner.json contains the expected rule

## GokuRakuJo DSL reference

### Basic remapping
\`\`\`clojure
[:a :b]                          ; a -> b
[:!Ca :b]                        ; Cmd+a -> b
[:!Oa :b]                        ; Opt+a -> b
[:!Ta :b]                        ; Ctrl+a -> b
