\`\`\`clojure
[:a :b [:app "Terminal"]]                   ; only in Terminal
[:a :b [:!app "Finder"]]                    ; everywhere except Finder
[:a :b [:input-source "com.apple.keylayout.US"]]  ; only US layout
\`\`\`

### Modifiers reference
- \`!\` = mandatory modifier: C=Cmd, O=Opt, T=Ctrl, S=Shift, F=Fn
- \`#\` = optional modifier: any combo of modifiers is allowed
- \`##\` = optional any modifier

